description:
Our place is a spacious, sunny 1 bedroom / 2 bathroom apartment located in prime Upper West Side, only one block from Central Park. On a high floor in an elevator building, it is ideal for couples and small families. You will find it well-furnished and fully equipped, close to great food and near major public transportation.

Take a peek at the photos and reach out with any questions. We are experienced members of the AirBnB community and look forward to welcoming you into our NYC home!

The Master Bedroom features a comfy Casper queen bed and open closet / drawer space. The Master Bathroom is well stocked, including a hairdryer. There is also a TV w/Roku (incl. ESPN, CNN, HBO etc. + Netflix) in addition to a work desk and monitor where you can plug in your laptop.

The Living Room is quite spacious with a queen sofa bed, dining table and 60" HDTV w/ Roku (incl. ESPN, CNN, HBO etc. + Netflix). Being on a high floor, you will be treated to fantastic sunset views over the Hudson river. The guest bathroom is well stocked and has a bathtub / shower. 

The Kitchen is fully equipped (microwave, stove, oven, dishwasher, pots, pans) and even features a Nespresso machine :)

The Building provides 24 hour doorman, elevators and a furnished outdoor courtyard

Keys are easily accessible with the 24/7 doorman, check-in times are flexible (depending on previous guests)

Our neighborhood in the Upper West Side is family friendly and close to great cafés, restaurants and museums…. not to mention Central Park is only one block away!

Subway: The B/C subway is a 3 min walk away and the 1/2/3 subway is a 6 min walk away

Example Travel Times (door-to-door):
Central Park / 3 min walk
Natural History Museum / 12 min walk
Lincoln Center / 14 mins subway (3 stops)
Times Square & Midtown / 16 mins subway (2 stops)
West Village & Greenwich Village / 22 mins subway (8 stops)
Metropolitan Museum of Art / 5 min taxi; 20 min walk

Our place is stocked with plenty of toiletries and household items, including European plug adapters, shampoo, conditioner, soap, bath gel, toilet tissue, blow dryer, iron, ironing board, umbrellas, first aid supplies, chargers, etc.  If you have special requests or require further information, please don't hesitate to contact me directly before booking.
